{
  "text": "Finally we applied our analysis to transcription profiles previously generated by Frank et al. [CITATION_1] and found the same switching pattern underlying their data (see Fig. S6 ). The fact that we can recapture the same pattern from two independently derived sets of data from different parasite genotypes and multiple independent clones strongly suggests that this particular pathway is an intrinsic feature of var gene switching.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "5138205"
